{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id7776769b-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s410jjj–3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"410jjj–3"},"text":"§ 410jjj–3.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Report","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Within three years from the effective date of this subchapter, the Secretary shall review the area within the park and shall report to the President, in accordance with subsections 1132(c) and (d) of this title, his recommendation as to the suitability or nonsuitability of any area within the park for preservation as wilderness, and any designation of any such area as wilderness shall be accomplished in accordance with said subsections.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id7776769c-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/545/s4"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–545, § 4","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-18"},"text":"Oct. 18, 1976","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/90/2518"},"text":"90 Stat. 2518","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/108/tI/s135"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–108, title I, § 135","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2003-11-10"},"text":"Nov. 10, 2003","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/117/1270"},"text":"117 Stat. 1270","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id7776769d-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id7776769e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id7776769f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The effective date of this subchapter, referred to in text, probably means the date of enactment of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/545"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–545","children":[],"tail":", which was approved on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1976-10-18"},"text":"Oct. 18, 1976","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"statutoryNotes","id":"id777676a0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"changeOfName","id":"id777676a1-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Change of Name","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"In text, “park” substituted for “monument” pursuant to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/108/s135"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–108, § 135","children":[],"tail":", which is set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s410jjj"},"text":"section 410jjj of this title","children":[],"tail":" and which redesignated the Congaree Swamp National Monument as the Congaree National Park."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
